body:
I referred @DiamondYuan comments in [dayjs/issues](https://github.com/iamkun/dayjs/issues/73)   and changed  the following code in filter.js
`const formatDate = (value, fmt) => {
  value = value.replace(/(\+\d{2})(\d{2})$/, "$1:$2");
  fmt = fmt || 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss'
  return dayjs(value).format(fmt)
}`
it's work well for me.
